{"h87e85415gced2g4757g9fa0g830c290b7549": ["Things are starting to calm down, thanks to you. We can finally get some rest.", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "b16affe8-e0ab-a7d9-8325-302d1944326a"], "h54c45878gde38g4e72gb475ge0609f0405f0": ["You look as tired as I feel.", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "44097c93-70b6-9f08-49f5-8fe83ed0fd32"], "hec5fc1e5g87f5g4cbfgbdeegb5c4d38ccf49": ["<i>Aggeniculamur in umbra</i>... did I say that out loud?", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "0c5dc563-9d55-0331-08ed-51d755b3bb92"], "h217610fcgc837g4861gb360g0b16b01cee40": ["We've been chanting for days. I need some rest.", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "5e07c39a-e49b-2510-e394-c64c5addeb69"], "h4a500db8g3930g41b0gb882g4d8b6a2d5b38": ["How long have you been there? Blessed Silvanus, I need to lie down.", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "fa3aa5e1-819a-d78b-e1c5-91bf7551955b"], "ha929e653g6ee0g4493ga14egc4bf1fd17fb0": ["<i>In umbram cretus, sanguine iuratus.</i>", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "0858efe2-4504-24ef-dc7f-f0a7c54e26cd"], "h79f3b322g99fdg4767g8616g745a00804f22": ["<i>Ab spiritu humoque, aculeus vitisque.</i>", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "fca94788-eed8-1d1e-9097-0b72c592640a"], "he83bf8b7gec7dg4e5cgb8dbge529bbe961d7": ["<i>Complexum tuum, ab terra ortum, ad nos defer.</i>", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "393ee57d-93f3-78d3-d488-d5bb0dc57c32"], "hbd4ecdc8g3b57g41ddga5ffgcff641712020": ["<i>Defende nos ab imminentibus aequilibrio tuo.</i>", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "a2d33d1c-6faf-80e5-f2e5-ab13faae5836"], "hb066fcbfg6b43g41cbga0e1g2001db4e57d7": ["<i>Hostes subeunt. Protege nos. Muni nos.</i>", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "3e203ec4-123e-bd92-a2a1-210d72fb0a1b"], "h96de5d1cg35c8g4d19gb7a1g5e7781726a20": ["<i>Aggeniculamur in umbra tua, Pater Arborum.</i>", "9c5c4c89-890b-4e72-8698-53d36e6b4271", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid1.html", "e6bb0fc3-99f6-d60f-028d-be3af9152860"]}